🔸 الحل 3: Docker محلي
────────────────────────

$ docker run -it \
  -v $(pwd)/config:/mount/admin \
  -e INSTALL_PATH=/mount/admin \
  my-app:latest

أو:

$ docker run -it \
  --mount type=bind,source=$(pwd)/config,target=/mount/admin \
  my-app:latest


